Paul Play and Nonso Amadi Nigerian singer Paul Play has released his second single for the year 2020 titled “Kolo” and he features Nonso Amadi on it. “Kolo” is coming after the release of the remix of his classic song “Angel of My Life” on which he featured Runtown. With “Kolo,” the veteran singer is stamping that he is indeed fully back to the music scene and fans can expect nothing but his best. Produced by Nonso A, “Kolo” is reminiscent of the sound from Paul Play’s 2007 hit “Forever”. However, by introducing the fresh voice of Nonso Amadi, the song has a new vibe to it and soulful appeal. Listen to “Kolo” below: